{"tid":707903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尾隨女子回家！樓梯間強脫衣裙　噁男被判3年","createTime":"2018-06-19T03:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T14:48:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6c61b1d434902d10e2aeb313a4aad5431ae2ed","tid":707903,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:19:07.000Z","msg":"小心變態色狼！<br />\n《聯合報》報導，新北市詹姓男子1月25日下午3點左右，看到一女子獨自走在街上，竟起了色心，尾隨她回住處，在公寓1樓、2樓的樓梯間，從後方抓住女子，強吻、撫胸，還想將她衣服、裙子脫下。<br />\n女子強力抵抗後，詹男無法得逞，悻然離去。被害人事後報警，詹男最後被法官判處3年徒刑，全案還可上訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/111854_12719abe7548dfd5a5c86a23a24d3efc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F111854_12719abe7548dfd5a5c86a23a24d3efc.png&h=5a8f4456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180619/1375672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180619%2F1375672&d=FlOzQurTqKnjmcvyDim7wTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ff93166a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180619%2F1375672&h=b9e1b375\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180619/1375672</a>"},{"pid":"92cb5ef2d0ea7f2f3a1188efe76263ced2b7983d","tid":707903,"uid":12468,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:20:55.000Z","msg":"得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9871832a0deda30647083222162fcec27744add","tid":707903,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:33:35.000Z","msg":"強姦埋都可能判4年到"},{"pid":"98be3c8839b3a7f6fac24293d50e73507f9bd4b5","tid":707903,"uid":3480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"大雄"},{"pid":"a6f8d28c2a4ad3ab29f2076604c79ce82f25bbb9","tid":707903,"uid":15,"like":12,"disl